@startuml
title 图6-2 库存出库时序图

actor 用户
participant "库存出库页面" as Page
participant "PostgREST" as Api
participant "scm.stock_out" as StockOut
database "scm.inventory_batches" as Batches
database "scm.inventory_transactions" as Tx

用户 -> Page : 选择批次并填写出库数量
Page -> Api : POST /rpc/scm.stock_out
Api -> StockOut : 调用出库函数
StockOut -> Batches : 锁定批次记录并读取可用库存
alt 库存不足
StockOut --> Api : 抛出库存不足异常
Api --> Page : 返回错误信息
Page --> 用户 : 提示出库失败
else 库存充足
StockOut -> Batches : 扣减 available_qty
StockOut -> Tx : 写入出库流水
StockOut --> Api : 返回剩余数量与结果
Api --> Page : 返回 JSON 结果
Page --> 用户 : 刷新库存并提示成功
end

@enduml
